      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].choice.optionA.label
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].choice.optionB.label
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].choice.optionA.label
      value: Accept
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].choice.optionB.label
      value: Accept
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].choice.optionA.label
      value: Retry?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].choice.optionB.label
      value: Give Up
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].choice.optionA.nextIndex
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].choice.optionB.nextIndex
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: "Well, if it isn\u2019t my favourite gambler! Now this is surprising."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[1].text
      value: "In all my years as head of this establishment, I don\u2019t think I\u2019ve
        ever seen anyone reach Salvation this quickly."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[2].text
      value: "You\u2019re one lucky bastard, huh?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[3].text
      value: "\u2026Or are you?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[4].text
      value: "See, here\u2019s the thing\u2026 I lied."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[5].text
      value: "Or, well, lie is not the word, I\u2019m no liar. I simply\u2026 Skimmed
        on some details."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[6].text
      value: "The truth is\u2026 There is no new life for you."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[7].text
      value: For you are already dead.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[8].text
      value: You expired in a dark alley due to a combination of hunger, thirst and
        exhaustion.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[9].text
      value: Sad and alone. With nothing to your name, with no goals to fulfill.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].choice.optionA.nextIndex
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].choice.optionB.nextIndex
      value: 2
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: You wasted your life on accomplishing and chasing nothing.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[1].text
      value: "That makes you\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[2].text
      value: A nobody.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[3].text
      value: "Ironic, isn\u2019t it?"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[4].text
      value: "Well, the irony doesn\u2019t end there."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[5].text
      value: "Like I said, I\u2019m no liar. I will give you a new life. A new beginning.
        A new body, a new face, a new name\u2026 And a new purpose."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[6].text
      value: I will give you mine.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[7].text
      value: "And I\u2026 Will be free."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[8].text
      value: And you will be stuck hosting this dreadful place until someone else
        takes your place, as will you take mine.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[9].text
      value: "So come on now. Don\u2019t distract me for much longer. The pearly
        gates are waiting for me."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[0].text
      value: "Ah\u2026 Now that\u2019s\u2026 Surprising. Really, it caught me off-guard."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[1].text
      value: I thought I had ya.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[2].text
      value: "But oh well, I\u2019m not pushy. Your choice is your choice."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[3].text
      value: Turn around and step back into the dark now. I wish you the best, buddy.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[4].text
      value: I really do.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[5].text
      value: After having wandered through the dirty streets for days on end with
        no shelter, no food and barely any water,; your body eventually gave up.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[6].text
      value: As you expire, you spend your last moments wondering where it all went
        wrong. What you could have done to change this outcome.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[2].lines.Array.data[7].text
      value: THE END
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[10].text
      value: You came and went, such as the breeze.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[11].text
      value: "Truly, you didn\u2019t add anything to society, and neither did you
        take away from it."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[12].text
      value: "But allow me to explain\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[13].text
      value: My casino is, in words you might understand it, purgatory.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[14].text
      value: A purgatory designed for people whose lives were spent unfulfilled.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[15].text
      value: In here, everyone chases Salvation as their new goal. And everyone takes
        the shape that best suits their soul.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[16].text
      value: "Some are sketches, because they never managed to make a plan for their
        life. They\u2019re an \u201Cunfinished product\u201D."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[17].text
      value: Some were led astray by their intrusive thoughts, and therefore here
        those thoughts materialized as a breathing creature looming over them.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[18].text
      value: "Some died for trusting blindly, getting baited. Some felt small their
        entire lives. Some thought technology could fix them, some felt like a hunk
        of muscle with a tiny brain\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[19].text
      value: "And you\u2026 You\u2019re just a shade."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[20].text
      value: "Undefined and blank. Because you have no characteristics, no traits\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[21].text
      value: "And you\u2026 You\u2019re just a shade."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[0].lines.Array.data[22].text
      value: "And you\u2026 You\u2019re just a shade."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[10].text
      value: "So come on now. Don\u2019t distract me for much longer. The pearly
        gates are waiting for me."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[11].text
      value: "Truly, you didn\u2019t add anything to society, and neither did you
        take away from it."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
      propertyPath: blocks.Array.data[1].lines.Array.data[12].text
      value: "But allow me to explain\u2026"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 6327419847685502032, guid: 604531e7ba8bf7d4d9f24973fb967ae3, type: 3}
